### Get Reservation Detail By Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/reservation/10
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Reservation By Reservation Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/reservation/lookup/RSV-27QWG7
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
Accept: application/json

### Change Reservation Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/reservation/change-status
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": 237,
  "reservationNumber": "RSV-EAKPVU",
  "reservationStatus": "CurrentEntrada",
  "personsToConfirm" : 1
}

### Update Reservation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/reservation/96
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "reservationId": 96,
  "details": {
    "serviceDate": "2026-02-18",
    "availabilityId": 13,
    "capacity": 6,
    "notes": "Cambiar a mesa interior, por favor",
    "cleaningTime": "00:15:00",
    "startTime": "08:00",
    "endTime": "09:00",
    "allergenIds": [1, 2]
  }
}

