### 4. Crear una Reserva Capturando varios Slots
# Aquí simulamos capturar un slot de reserva (ID 1) y su cleaning (ID 2).
# Debes obtener IDs reales del paso anterior.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/reservation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{admin_jwt}}

{
  "consumptionCenterId": 1,
  "details": {
    "capacity": 2,
    "notes": "Prueba de reserva con slots físicos",
    "createdBy": "Sistema",
    "availabilityIds": [1217,1218,1219],
    "employeeCode": "EMP001",
    "reservationDetailPersons": [
      {
        "name": "Juan Pérez",
        "age": 30,
        "personType": "Adulto",
        "personNumber": 1
      },
      {
        "name": "Eva Perez",
        "age": 25,
        "personType": "Adulto",
        "personNumber": 1
      }
    ]
  }
}

